{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}Then, in the day that the {\scaps Lord} gives you rest from your toil and turmoil and from the hard service that was{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}laid upon you, you will take up this taunt-song over the King of Babylon, and say:
