{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and sprung from the loins of Judah,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
who swear by the name of the {\scaps Lord},
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and celebrate Israel\uc1\u8217*s God \uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
but neither with justice or truth;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}for they call themselves after the holy city,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and lean on the God of Israel,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
whose name is the {\scaps Lord} of Hosts.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}Of old I announced predictions,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and uttered them forth from my lips:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
of a sudden I wrought, and they came.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}But I knew that you were stubborn,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
with a neck like an iron band,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and a forehead all of brass;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}so I told it you long ago:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
ere it came to pass, I informed you:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
in case you should claim that your idol had wrought it,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
your images \uc1\u8211* molten or graven \uc1\u8211* appointed it.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}You have heard it, now see it fulfilled;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
wilt you not bear witness to it?
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs48 The Restoration of Israel and the Future Glory of Zion

\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs36 The servant discouraged, but at last triumphant

\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs36 The servant: his seeming failure and his great destiny

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1\f1\fs22 49}Hearken, you isles, unto me,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and you peoples from far, give attention.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
The {\scaps Lord} has called me from birth,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
from the womb of my mother he gave me my name.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}Like a sharp sword made he my mouth,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
in the shadow of his hand did he hide me;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
he made me a polished shaft,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
in his quiver he concealed me.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}And he said to me, \uc1\u8220*You are my servant,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
in whom I will show my glory;\uc1\u8221*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}But I said, \uc1\u8220*I have laboured in vain,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
I have spent my strength on an empty nothing;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
yet safe is my cause with the {\scaps Lord},
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and my recompense with my God.\uc1\u8221*
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}And now \uc1\u8211* thus says the {\scaps Lord},
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
who formed me from birth for his servant,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
to bring Jacob back unto him,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and that Israel to him might be gathered \uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and so I had honour in the sight of the {\scaps Lord},
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
my God became my strength.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}He says, \uc1\u8220*It is too light a thing
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
to raise up the tribes of Jacob,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and Israel\uc1\u8217*s dispersed to restore:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
I will make you a light to the nations,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
that so my salvation may reach
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
to the very ends of the earth.\uc1\u8221*
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs36 Israel\uc1\u8217*s happy return and restoration

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}Thus says the (true) God the {\scaps Lord},
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Israel\uc1\u8217*s holy redeemer,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
to him who of men is contemned,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
abhorred of the nations, the servant of tyrants:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
kings, when they see you, will rise,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and princes will bow down in homage,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
because of the {\scaps Lord} the faithful,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and Israel\uc1\u8217*s Holy One, who chose you.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}Thus says the {\scaps Lord}:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
now will I favour and answer you,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
now will I help and deliver you;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
making you pledge and symbol
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
of my covenant with mankind:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
restoring the (ruined) land,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and allotting the desolate heritage;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}bidding the prisoners go forth,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and the inmates of darkness to show themselves.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
They will pasture wherever they go,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
even on all the bare hills will be pasture;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 10}they will neither hunger nor thirst,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
neither sun nor the hot wind will smite them.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
For one who pities will lead them,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and guide them to foundations of water.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}I will make all the mountains a highway,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and roads will be raised everywhere.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}Lo! Yonder they come from afar,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
some from the north and the west,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and some from the land of Syene.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 13}Sing, O you heavens, for joy;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and earth, do you exult;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
let the mountains break forth into song.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
For the {\scaps Lord} comforts his folk,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
takes pity upon his affected.
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs36 The consolation of Zion

\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs36 Wasted Zion will be rebuilt and repeopled

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 14}\uc1\u8220*But the {\scaps Lord},\uc1\u8221* says Zion, \uc1\u8220*has left me;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
my Lord has forgotten me clean.\uc1\u8221*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 15}Can a woman forget her babe,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
cease to pity the son of her womb?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Yes, such may indeed forget,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
but never will I forget you.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 16}I have graven you on my hands,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and your walls are for ever before me:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 17}in haste men are coming to build you;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
while those who have torn you down
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and laid you in ruins, will leave you.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 18}Lift up your eyes round about, and behold
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
how they flock to you, all of them gathered together.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Yea, thus says the {\scaps Lord} on oath, as I live,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
you will wear them upon you as jewels on a garment,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and bind them about you as bride binds her girdle.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 19}For your desolate wastes and your ruined land
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
(will be turned to a garden and crowded with men.)
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Then scarce room enough you will have for your people,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
when those who devoured you are far away.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 20}The children you long were bereft of
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
will one day declare in your ears,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
\uc1\u8220*This place is too narrow for me,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
give me ampler space to dwell in.\uc1\u8221*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 21}And then you will say in your heart,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
\uc1\u8220*Who can have borne me these children?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Since I am bereaved and unfruitful,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
who can have reared these children?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Behold! I was left all alone:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
who then can these children be?\uc1\u8221*
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs36 Three words of consolation

\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs36 At a signal from the Lord, the nations will bring Israel back to Zion

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 22}Thus says the Lord the {\scaps Lord}:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
behold I will lift up my hand to the nations,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and raise for the people my banner (as signal);
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and then they will bring your sons in their bosom,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and carry your daughters upon their shoulders.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 23}Kings will be your foster-fathers,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and queens will be your nursing mothers;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
with face to the earth they will do you homage,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and lick the dust of your feet:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and then you will know that I am the {\scaps Lord},
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
who never will bring those who trust me to shame.
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs36 The Lord is omnipotent

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 24}Can prey from the mighty be wrenched,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
or can captives escape from a tyrant?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 25}Verily, thus says the {\scaps Lord}:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
yes, even from the mighty can captives be wrenched,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and the prey of a tyrant escape;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
but {\i I} will defend your cause,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
{\i I} will deliver your children,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 26}and cause your oppressors to eat their own flesh,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and to drink themselves drunk with their blood as with wine.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
And then all flesh will know
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
that I am your saviour-redeemer,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
the {\scaps Lord}, the Strong One of Jacob.
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs36 The Lord\uc1\u8217*s omnipotent love

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1\f1\fs22 50}Thus says the {\scaps Lord}:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
where is the bill of your mother\uc1\u8217*s divorcement,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
wherewith I have put her away?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Or which of my creditors is it
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
to whom I have ever sold you?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
If sold you have been, \uc1\u8217*tis because of your sins;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
your rebellions have led to your mother\uc1\u8217*s divorce.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}Why, when I came, was there no one,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and none to respond when I called?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Is my hand too short to deliver?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
And have I no power to rescue?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
With a word of a rebuke did I dry up the sea,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and rivers I turned into desert;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
their fish dried up for lack of water,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
their monsters perished on thirsty land.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}I clothed the heavens in mourning,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and sackcloth I made their covering.
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs36 The servant tried but trusting

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}The Lord the {\scaps Lord} has given me
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
the tongue of a true disciple,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
to know how to answer the weary
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
with words (of consolation).
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
In the morning he opens my ears
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
to listen, as true disciple;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}as for me, I have not been rebellious,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
or turned me backward away.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}I gave my back to the lash,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and my cheeks unto those who plucked them;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
my face and I did not hide
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
from insult or from spitting.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}For the Lord of the {\scaps Lord} helps me,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and so I am not confounded;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
I set my face like a flint,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and I know I will never be shamed.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}My vindicator is nigh,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
who then dare to contend with me?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Let us both stand up together.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Who dare be my opponent?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Let him draw nigh unto me.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}See, the {\scaps Lord} God is my helper;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
where, then, is the man who can worst me?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
They all like a garment will crumble,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
the moth will eat them up.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 10}Let that man among you who fears the {\scaps Lord}
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
listen to the voice of his servant.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Whoso walks in darkness,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
with not a gleam of light,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
let him trust in the name of the {\scaps Lord},
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and lean upon his God.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}All you who kindle a fire,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and you who set brands aflame,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
