\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
I hid my eyes in silence,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and me you did not fear.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}But I will expose your doings,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
this \uc1\u8220*righteousness\uc1\u8221* of yours.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

