{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs36 Fasting

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1\f1\fs22 58}Cry with full throat and refrain not,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
