\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}Daily indeed they consult me,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
their joy is to learn my ways,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
like a nation that does the right
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and forsaken not the law of its God.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
They ask me to guide then aright,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
they delight to draw nigh unto God.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}\uc1\u8220*Why look you not when we fast?\uc1\u8221* (they say)
