\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
you drive all your workmen like slaves.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}See! you fast for strife and contention,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
