{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
is this what you call a fast,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
a day that the {\scaps Lord} accepts?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}Thus says the Lord the {\scaps Lord}:
