{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Your strength he will make new again,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and you like a well-watered garden will be,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
