\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
they trust in pretence and lies,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
conceive trouble and bring forth mischief.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
