\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
for evil is what they fabricate,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
their hands work deeds of violence.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}Their feet run to evil,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
they haste to shed innocent blood;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
their thoughts are thoughts of mischief,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
their paths are wreck and ruin.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}The ways of peace they know not,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
no justice is in their tracks:
\par}

